  "text": "Among participants with detectable HR-HPV at baseline, we observed that EBV shedding was associated with significantly reduced likelihood of HR-HPV clearing during the following 48 weeks. This is in line with a previous report suggesting that EBV might be associated with higher risk of HR-HPV integration into the human genome [CITATION_1] , which is an important step in the development of invasive carcinoma.",
